<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Patch>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Vanilla Fishing Expanded - Fishing Treasures AddOn</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/TraitDef[defName="OEFishermanVCEF"]/degreeDatas/li[1]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>심해 낚시꾼</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/TraitDef[defName="OEFishermanVCEF"]/degreeDatas/li[1]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>{PAWN_nameDef}(은)는 신중하고 집중력 있게 낚시를 하며, 낚싯대를 던질 때마다 더 많은 수확을 거둡니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
        
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/TraitDef[defName="OEFishermanVCEF"]/degreeDatas/li[2]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>빠른 챔질</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/TraitDef[defName="OEFishermanVCEF"]/degreeDatas/li[2]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>{PAWN_nameDef}(은)는 낚싯대를 자주, 빠르게 던지지만 일부 물고기를 놓치기도 합니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
</Patch>